 <h1>Getting to know open access</h1>
 Making images of your public domain artworks openly available can significantly increase how your collections are seen, used, and understood.

The section is designed to prepare you and your organisation to understand open access and the standards used on the Art UK platform. It may also be useful as an introduction to open access more broadly. 

